    p We received a request to reset your password. If you made this request, please click the button below to set a new password:

    - const resetUrl = `${EMAIL_URL}/auth/reset-password?token=${token}`

    a(
      href=resetUrl
      style="display:inline-block;padding:12px 20px;background-color:#4f46e5;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;border-radius:6px;font-weight:bold;"
    )
      | Reset Password

